    <h1>THE <span class=3D"g">GREENING</span><br><span class=3D"b">DIVIDE</=
span></h1>
    <p class=3D"sub">Satellites show large parts of the Earth getting green=
er since 2000. This explorer asks the harder question: <strong>who gets the=
 greening?</strong> Vegetation trends (NDVI), 2000=E2=80=932024, split by W=
orld Bank income group.</p>
    <p class=3D"auth"><strong>Sonali Singh</strong> =C2=B7 [add original DS=
C 106 teammates before publishing]</p>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"scrollcue">Scroll =E2=86=93</div>
