<section><div class=3D"wrap">
  <p class=3D"eyebrow">Chapter 1 =C2=B7 Context</p>
  <h2>The Earth is greening =E2=80=94 that part isn't controversial</h2>
  <p class=3D"lede">Two decades of satellite vegetation records show widesp=
read increases in leaf area and greenness across the planet, driven by CO=
=E2=82=82 fertilization, warming in cold regions, and =E2=80=94 heavily =E2=
=80=94 agricultural intensification. Global averages, though, are where ine=
quality hides. This project splits the same signal by the World Bank's inco=
me groups and watches the lines diverge.</p>
</div></section>

<section style=3D"padding-top:20px"><div class=3D"wrap">
  <p class=3D"eyebrow">Chapter 2 =C2=B7 The globe</p>
