=80=932005: the baseline</h3><p>Every country's greening is measured agains=
t its own early-2000s average, so the map starts near neutral. Color =3D pe=
rcent change in NDVI vs that baseline.</p></div></div>
      <div class=3D"step" data-step=3D"1"><div class=3D"card"><h3>Sweep to =
2024</h3><p>As the years advance, green deepens where vegetation gained and=
